      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of June 13 obituary about Michaela Odone</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An obituary last Tuesday about Michaela Odone, co-developer of Lorenzo's oil to treat adrenoleukodystrophy, a rare degenerative children's disease, misstated the abbreviation by which the disease is known. It is ALD, not ADL.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
